<mjml>
   <mj-include path="../../template_components/_globals.mjml" /> <!-- globals -->
   <mj-body background-color="#F1F5FB">
   <mj-include path="../../template_components/header/headerLogo.mjml" /> <!-- Header Logo Include -->
      
   <mj-wrapper padding="0 15px">
      <mj-section 
         background-color="#4e4c64"
         border-radius="15px"
         padding="0px">
            <mj-column width="65%">
               <mj-image
                  src="./img/header-text.png"
                  alt="Welcome to 22seven"
                  padding-top="70px"
                  width="400px"
                  align="center"/>
            </mj-column>
            <mj-column width="35%">
               <mj-image
                  align="center"
                  src="./img/man.png"
                  alt="Welcome to 22seven"
                  padding="0px 20px 0px 0px"
                  width="150px"/>
            </mj-column>
         </mj-section> <!-- Plain Section -->
      </mj-wrapper>

      <mj-section /> <!-- Spacer -->

      <mj-wrapper padding="0 15px">
         <mj-section mj-class="section" padding="15px 0px" >
            <mj-column>
               <mj-text mj-class="title">
                     Try to check in once a week.
               </mj-text>
               <mj-text mj-class="sectionText--normal">
                  We know that the more people engage with their money, the better they are with it. Some people check in on 22seven every day. But even weekly is probably going to have some very positive consequences. At the very least, we suggest you check in once a month. 
               </mj-text>
               <mj-image
                  align="center"
                  src="./img/calender.png"
                  alt="Get Debt Free Icon"
                  width="385px"/>
            </mj-column>
         </mj-section> <!-- Plain Section -->
      </mj-wrapper>

      <mj-section /> <!-- spacer -->

      <mj-wrapper padding="5px 15px">
         <mj-section  mj-class="section">
            <mj-column width="100%" padding="0px 0px 10px">
               <mj-text mj-class="title">
                  Keep Automatic Account Updates on.
               </mj-text>
            </mj-column>

            <mj-column width="100%">
               <mj-image
               align="center"
                  src="./img/platforms.png"
                  alt="Get Debt Free Icon"
                 />

               <mj-text mj-class="sectionText--normal">
                 This way, you know that your linked accounts are updated for you, every day, without you having to do anything. And that means youâ€™ll never lose any transactions. (Some account updates only go back 30 days, so if you leave a month between log-ins, you risk losing older transactions.)
                  <br/><br/>
                  Remember, you can choose what time you want the updates to happen. 
                  <br/><br/>
               </mj-text>
               <mj-button
                  href="*|BASE_URL|*app/settings/auto-account-update?utm_source=*|MAIL_NAME|*&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=InService"
                  border-radius="20px"
                  background-color="#27C5B8"
                  width="85%"
               >
                  Choose a time for your Automatic Updates on Automatic Updates
               </mj-button>
            </mj-column> <!-- Get Debt Free -->

          
      </mj-wrapper>

      <mj-section /> <!-- spacer -->
      
      <mj-include path="../../template_components/footer/footer.mjml" /> <!-- Footer Include -->
   </mj-body>
</mjml>